<h2>Another ASCII Gnu</h2>

<pre>
  ,= ,-_-. =.
 ((_/)o o(\_))
  `-'(. .)`-'
      \_/
</pre>

<p>
This is an ASCII drawing of a gnu's head.  It fits into four lines
of text, the maximum length of email and usenet signatures.
</p>

<p>
